{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idcaee1b22-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s11702"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"11702"},"text":"§ 11702.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Enforcement by the Board","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Board may bring a civil action—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcaee1b23-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s11702/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" to enjoin a rail carrier from violating sections 10901 through 10906 of this title, or a regulation prescribed or order or certificate issued under any of those sections;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcaee1b24-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s11702/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" to enforce subchapter II of chapter 113 of this title and to compel compliance with an order of the Board under that subchapter; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcaee1b25-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s11702/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" to enforce an order of the Board, except a civil action to enforce an order for the payment of money, when it is violated by a rail carrier providing transportation subject to the jurisdiction of the Board under this part.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idcaee1b26-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/88/tI/s102/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–88,